  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">DeafTawk - Empower the Deaf community by providing quality sign language interpretation service through digital technology</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Further develop DeafTawk&apos;s existing mobile application by adding an AI bot feature that will enable the application to automatically interpret voice/text into sign language for the hearing-impaired users. Moreover, in partnership with an MNO (Jazz), DeafTawk will launch the Voice over IP (VoIP) service which will enable deaf users to converse using their smartphone with someone who uses a feature phone. Deaftawk will also use this grant to launch a training programme for interpreters and an awareness programme to educate users on how to use Deaftawk mobile application for sign language interpretation service.</narrative>
  </description>
